Nyabuka asipdeiyikba, Baruk birye tamubuka nyabuk. “Diba asekse yupu nirya ara, nabi Yeremia birye nyapdeibukop ura, adib aryuk el nyabuk ning uk sekse. Na ara, sekne ning ap, sekne mek ap, aning uk dobuka, akitildongon buku deice uk sekse. Abopmanba eipmalum ara, akunuma,” nyabuk.
Yeremia bira tapu koubuka, awenena aik bukni, tuku fum bisik dongobikce, Yeremia bira, atuku fum kikinak unmok. Asukum ara, ouku weik arye atuku fum tam ulamuk.
Tonda winipmanto, nun bitinye talipmanam yupu nirya, sik yuk nang kekenmacak nyapminye ura, sik anang arye yupu bobuka, na amutam fil don ati, weik deiyok nang ton, sik dam nyabikiba, kekebikirye, an dam yakirye, ‘An ap amutuku ninye deiyoknye ap talepmarum yupu ara, nun dam laka nyapsilyame. Ayupu laka kum nyapsiminye ura, nunce an ti oplopnamkiyabe,’ nyapnamakiya ati nyapkine.”
